measurements.description:
Fourteen flowers on one 72-cm upright inflorescence;
	sepals and petals off-white, lightly striated longitudinally rose speckles, denser distally;
	lip white overlaid broad burgundy band distally, burgundy center-stripe band to keels, side lobes 1-cm rose band, 
	keels yellow, lightly spotted burgundy;
	column white, blushed rose, ventral surface spotted burgundy, anther cap yellow;

	substance firm; texture matte.
